name: Personalliggare
description: SmartDok Personalliggare r en app som gr det mjligt fr underentreprenrer att registrera sig p en SmartDok-baserad personalliggare via sin mobil eller surfplatta.  Tjnsten r speciellt framtagen fr SmartDoks kunder som ett komplement till vra registreringsboxar.   SmartDok r en ackrediterad leverantr av personalliggare fr ID06 av Sveriges Byggindustrier. SmartDok Personnel Giver is an app that enables subcontractors to sign up for a SmartDok-based personal lier via their mobile or tablet. The service is specially designed for SmartDok customers as a complement to our registration boxes.  SmartDok is an accredited supplier of ID06 personal lighters by the Swedish Construction Industries.
